The doomgeneric_Create function will:
1. Set myargc = 0, myargv = 0
2. Call M_FindResponseFile()
3. Allocate DG_ScreenBuffer
4. Call DG_Init()
5. Call D_DoomMain()

D_DoomMain will initialize everything and then enter the main game loop.

The DG_DrawFrame function will save frames as BMP files to /tmp/frame.bmp.

